Class TransportationExpense

java.lang.Object
  edu.umn.se.trap.data.TransportationExpense
All Implemented Interfaces:
ExpenseWithCurrencyIface
public class TransportationExpense
extends java.lang.Object
implements ExpenseWithCurrencyIface

An object to hold all information related to transportation expenses. Not all fields will be set for every type of transportation expense so it is up to the user of this object to check.

Author:
andrewh
